pha.com/symbol/CELH\" class=\"ticker-link\" target=\"_blank\">CELH</a>) in July where I initiated a \u201cbuy\u201d rating with a price target of $66. With the stock down 47% from its May 2024 high <em>(at the time</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/93296103/image_93296103.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747559-celsius-my-contrarian-pick-for-2025", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 03:01:53", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747557", "title": "Federal Reserve Watch: Quantitative Tightening Continues", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Thoughtful man sitting down. Confusion and overthinking concept.\" data-id=\"1349363964\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"853px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Mihaela Rosu</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The Federal Reserve continued its program of quantitative tightening through the end of 2024.</p> <p>In the latest banking week, the Federal Reserve oversaw a $30.0 billion reduction in its securities portfolio.</p> <p>Since the program of quantitative tightening</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1349363964/image_1349363964.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747557-federal-reserve-watch-quantitative-tightening-continues", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 02:31:08", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747555", "title": "Why 2025 Could Be Another Blockbuster Year", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business Planning\" data-id=\"175599141\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5616px\" height=\"3744px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">blackred</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Despite fizzling out toward the end, 2024 was another blockbuster year for stocks. The S&amp;P 500 appreciated by 23.3%, and the Nasdaq composite achieved an impressive gain of 28.6%. Due to this constructive market dynamic, advantageous positioning, diversification, and other factors, our All-Weather Portfolio \"AWP\" increased by 69% in 2024</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/175599141/image_175599141.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747555-why-2025-could-be-another-blockbuster-year", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 02:20:43", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747554", "title": "Pop Goes The Tesla (Our Top Short For 2025)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young businesswoman charging her electric car at EV charging station\" data-id=\"2159481801\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Images By Tang Ming Tung</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Tesla, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TSLA\" title=\"Tesla, Inc.\">TSLA</a></span>) is a company we've discussed as overvalued for a while. Most recently, we discussed in <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741508-tesla-upcoming-government-double-whammy\">our article here</a>, about the potential impact of new government regulations. However, despite our negative</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2159481801/image_2159481801.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747554-pop-goes-the-tesla-our-top-short-for-2025", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 02:10:08", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747553", "title": "URA: Demand Growth Is Outweighed By Production Issues", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"West Burton power stations, UK\" data-id=\"2165931526\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">CHUNYIP WONG</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Today, nuclear power is seen as a low-carbon energy source producing almost zero carbon dioxide or other greenhouse gas emissions. Uranium is a huge component and the biggest driver for the future of nuclear energy.</p> <p>Global X</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2165931526/image_2165931526.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747553-ura-demand-growth-is-outweighed-by-production-issues", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 02:04:39", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747551", "title": "Volvo May Take A Hit In 2025, But Investors Can Still Come Out Ahead", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/12715219