ekingalpha.com/article/4747551-volvo-may-take-a-hit-in-2025-but-investors-can-still-come-out-ahead", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:52:59", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747549", "title": "Larimar Therapeutics: Positive Friedreich's Ataxia Data Can Only Get Better", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Rear view and close up image of Young Scientist researcher stirs the substance in the beaker while discussing the result with a colleague\" data-id=\"2177260462\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Pranithan Chorruangsak/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The last time I wrote about <b>Larimar Therapeutics, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/LRMR\" title=\"Larimar Therapeutics, Inc.\">LRMR</a></span>) it was in a <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4696828-larimar-stronger-buy-now-more-than-ever-after-partial-clinical-hold-completely-removed\">Seeking Alpha article</a> entitled \"<strong>Larimar: Stronger Buy Now More Than Ever After Partial Clinical Hold Completely</strong></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2177260462/image_2177260462.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747549-larimar-therapeutics-positive-friedreichs-ataxia-data-can-only-get-better", "pub_date": "2025-01-04 01:49:02", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747546", "title": "JPIE: A Long-Term Income ETF", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stack of coins from low to high,tiny men on top\" data-id=\"571606663\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/571606663/image_571606663.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/